In [ ]:
add_seq = "".join([v.code for v in alignm[0].residues]) + "..."

alignm=modeller.alignment(env)
alignm.append_sequence(add_seq)

alignm[0].code = "ligand"

mdl = modeller.model(env, file='1lmp.pdb')
alignm.append_model(mdl, atom_files='1lmp.pdb', align_codes='1lmp')

alignm.salign()
alignm.write(file='all_in_one_model_ligand.ali', alignment_format='PIR')

s = alignm[0]
pdb = alignm[1]

## Создаем объект automodel
a = modeller.automodel.automodel(env, alnfile='all_in_one_model_ligand.ali', knowns= pdb.code , sequence = s.code )

a.name='mod'+s.code
a.starting_model = 1
a.ending_model = 2
a.make()
